sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Chatbot Controller
    participant G as Content Guard
    participant CL as Classifier
    participant K as Knowledge Service
    participant V as Vector Store
    participant AI as AiProvider Cascade
    participant DB as SQL Server

    U->>C: POST /api/chatbot/message
    C->>G: isQuerySafe
    C->>CL: classify question
    alt University question
        C->>K: hybrid retrieval
        K->>V: vector search
        K->>DB: keyword search KnowledgeChunks
        K-->>C: RRF merged context
    end
    C->>AI: generateResponse
    AI-->>C: assistant text
    C->>DB: save ChatMessages
    C-->>U: JSON response
